
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>The Shisha Drop</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500&display=swap');
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #111;
      color: #f0e6d2;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 200%;
      height: 100%;
      background: url('https://i.imgur.com/zr0qsTg.gif') repeat-x center/cover;
      opacity: 0.08;
      animation: smokeMove 60s linear infinite;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    @keyframes smokeMove {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px 20px;
    }
    header img {
      max-width: 300px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 20px 40px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #c4b27c;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    }
    .hero p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #d6caa2;
    }
    .pricing {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .pricing h2 {
      color: #c4b27c;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .pricing .package-box {
      background-color: #222;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      width: 300px;
      margin: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .package-box h3 {
      color: #c4b27c;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .package-box img {
      height: 24px;
    }
    .package-box ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .contact {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .contact h2 {
      color: #c4b27c;
    }
    .contact p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #e0d7b3;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #0e0e0e;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <img src="the shisha drop.png" alt="The Shisha Drop Logo">
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Instant Atmosphere, Just Add Friends</h1>
    <p>The Shisha Drop delivers premium mobile shisha setups straight to your door — whether it's for personal relaxation, small gatherings, or stylish events across North London and Hertfordshire. We bring the lounge experience to your home or venue, with everything handled for you.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="pricing">
    <h2>Packages</h2>
    <div class="package-box">
      <h3><img src="shisha-icon.png" alt="Shisha Icon"> Standard Package</h3>
      <p><strong>£40</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>1 Shisha</li>
        <li>1 Flavour</li>
        <li>10 Coals</li>
        <li>2 Plastic Tips</li>
        <li>Disposable Pipe</li>
        <li>Coal Burner Rental</li>
        <li>Delivery & Collection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="package-box">
      <h3><img src="shisha-icon.png" alt="Shisha Icon"><img src="shisha-icon.png" alt="Shisha Icon"> Double Package</h3>
      <p><strong>£75</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>2 Shishas</li>
        <li>2 Flavours</li>
        <li>20 Coals</li>
        <li>4 Plastic Tips</li>
        <li>2 Disposable Pipes</li>
        <li>1 Coal Burner</li>
        <li>Delivery & Collection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="package-box">
      <h3><img src="shisha-icon.png" alt="Shisha Icon"><img src="shisha-icon.png" alt="Shisha Icon"><img src="shisha-icon.png" alt="Shisha Icon"> Triple Package</h3>
      <p><strong>£110</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>3 Shishas</li>
        <li>3 Flavours</li>
        <li>30 Coals</li>
        <li>6 Plastic Tips</li>
        <li>3 Disposable Pipes</li>
        <li>1 Coal Burner</li>
        <li>Delivery & Collection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Extras</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Extra Flavour/Head: <strong>£15</strong> (includes 10 complimentary coals)</li>
      <li>Extra Charcoal: <strong>10 coals for £2.50</strong></li>
      <li>Event Packages: <strong>from £100</strong> (tailored quotes available)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="contact">
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:bookings@theshishadrop.co.uk">bookings@theshishadrop.co.uk</a></p>
    <p>Instagram: <a href="https://instagram.com/theshishadrop" target="_blank">@TheShishaDrop</a></p>
    <p>Phone: 07400 123 456</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 The Shisha Drop. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
